  "detailed_description": "<h1>GAMES BY THE CREATOR OF CATO</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Cato, the cat is a casual match-3 game where you have to take care of your pet.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/1caf9860c66687541b07eb51a892968c.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/1caf9860c66687541b07eb51a892968c.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/1caf9860c66687541b07eb51a892968c.mp4?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You have to take care of Cato, a very smart cat, through a match-3 mechanic, don't let him get away, for that you'll have to feed him, quench his thirst and give him lots of love and fun.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to play</strong></h2><strong>Select a piece, you can use the spacebar key to rotate the piece, then place it on the board.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b4a9dcca32a64be6ffa7a74b3f15aecc.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b4a9dcca32a64be6ffa7a74b3f15aecc.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b4a9dcca32a64be6ffa7a74b3f15aecc.mp4?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Match 3 pieces or</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b6acaeb80cc0f8c56a94edbcc15bcfeb.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b6acaeb80cc0f8c56a94edbcc15bcfeb.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/b6acaeb80cc0f8c56a94edbcc15bcfeb.mp4?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>more of the same type horizontally or </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/be1a1b7df9a08e92c870db2e8fa9e8dc.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/be1a1b7df9a08e92c870db2e8fa9e8dc.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/be1a1b7df9a08e92c870db2e8fa9e8dc.mp4?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>vertically</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/ed5af5b915ccc57c853427b1db150a18.poster.avif?t=1681821138\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/ed5af5b915ccc57c853427b1db150a18.webm?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745710/extras/ed5af5b915ccc57c853427b1db150a18.mp4?t=1681821138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>ENJOY!</strong>",
